What you need to know:

The President also said that many times when we talk about gender equity we are referring to men, however, men in sports have and are also victims of gender-based violence.“The safe sports environment we are looking forward to creating should be for both men and women. My government is determined to promote gender equity in sport. I hope that by the end of this conference, you will present to the country and the world at large a commendable roadmap to tackle gender bias in sports,” he said. 